title: Sofia Richie dons peek-a-boob in sheer top – as romance with Lewis Hamilton is 'confirmed'
text:
TEEN STYLE QUEEN: Sofia opted for a sultry sheer top for the Topshop Unique show 
And she's doing it one risqué outfit at a time. 
The model pulled a show-stopping look out of the bag for Topshop Unique's London Fashion Week show at the Tate Modern in London. 
The blonde beauty rocked a shocking see-through turtle neck which revealed her peek-a-boo lace bra underneath. 
GETTY PEEK-A-BOOB LACE: Sofia covered up with a PVC coat 
But Sofia's lace bra was also seriously sheer, revealing her nipples beneath. 
We wonder what dad, Lionel Richie would think of this one… 
The 18-year-old teamed her brazen boob-baring outfit with on trend camo trousers and a PVC coat. Justin Bieber's dating history We take a look at the hottest girls that pop sensation Justin Bieber has dated. 1 / 26 
GETTY CAMO CUTIE: Sofia is keen to make her mark on the modelling industry 
While the style queen put her most fashionable foot forward in a pair of black heeled boots. 
But the young fashionista seemed to go it alone for the event, without rumoured boyfriend Lewis Hamilton in tow.
